_fzjcUOHFwHlIw">Trúng số thi kỳ 2 - 中數詩其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/author-IGETeQBwf_c0CasyF8dTBQ">Trần Đình Tân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/V%C4%83n-m%E1%BB%87nh-b%E1%BA%AFc-s%E1%BB%A9-l%C6%B0u-gi%E1%BA%A3n-kinh-trung-ch%C6%B0-h%E1%BB%AFu/poem-6STYMTu8I4oruA2sdmPBuA">Văn mệnh bắc sứ lưu giản kinh trung chư hữu - 聞命北使留簡京中諸友</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/author-YFWZ8afu7g2IoLevX1_E2Q">Nguyễn Đề</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Huy-O%C3%A1nh/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-nZpuYY0I_gKn_a148N9zWA">Vô đề - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Huy-O%C3%A1nh/author-dr5ryihj5N63kZ-8HnRW6A">Nguyễn Huy Oánh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/Y-ch%E1%BB%89/poem-hfxf9MFdYeILmDjAt8Fhew">Y chỉ - 醫旨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/author-IGETeQBwf_c0CasyF8dTBQ">Trần Đình Tân</a>)<br></div>	</div>
